    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">From billed-not-banked to collection-based books.</h2>
    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">Every healthcare engagement follows the same four-phase rhythm &mdash; built so your books are accurate before anyone tries to advise on them.</p>
