    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 24px;max-width:72ch;">A single claim moves through five different figures before it&rsquo;s real revenue. Bookkeeping that records only the deposit &mdash; or only the charge &mdash; misses where the money actually went.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
      <caption class="sr-only">How a billed charge becomes collected revenue in a medical practice</caption>
      <thead><tr><th scope="col">Figure</th><th scope="col" class="num us">What it is</th><th scope="col">Where it belongs in the books</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        {%- for r in billedCollected %}
